<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/neither-democrats-nor-republicans-will-admit-the-problem-is-capitalism-itself/">Neither Democrats Nor Republicans Will Admit the Problem Is Capitalism Itself</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Cycles of growth followed by downturns is how capitalism has functioned for 250 years.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
