<div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
<a class="archive-image" href="https://truthout.org/articles/the-covid-19-pandemic-is-exposing-the-plague-of-neoliberalism/" title="The COVID-19 Pandemic Is Exposing the Plague of Neoliberalism">
<img width="400" height="300" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2020_0407-coronavirus-neoliberalism-g-400x300.jpg" class="attachment-sd_medium size-sd_medium" alt="Stock traders in facemasks watch markets crash in horror" loading="lazy" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2020_0407-coronavirus-neoliberalism-g-400x300.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2020_0407-coronavirus-neoliberalism-g-200x150.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2020_0407-coronavirus-neoliberalism-g-800x600.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2020_0407-coronavirus-neoliberalism-g-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/2020_0407-coronavirus-neoliberalism-g-2400x1800.jpg 2400w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" />
